# TMA Studio - Root Environment Variables
# This file documents all environment variables used across the monorepo
# Copy component-specific .env.example files to .env in each directory

# See apps/web/.env.example for web app configuration
# See apps/api/.env.example for API configuration
# See apps/bot/.env.example for bot configuration

# Quick Reference:
# - BOT_TOKEN: Get from @BotFather on Telegram
# - DATABASE_URL: Supabase Postgres connection string
# - JWT_SECRET: Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
# - PUBLIC_API_URL: API endpoint for frontend
# - WEB_APP_URL: Mini App URL for bot
